  <brief_title>Renal Replacement Therapy Plus Extracorporeal Carbon Dioxide Removal</brief_title>
  <official_title>Combined Strategy of Renal Replacement Therapy Plus Extracorporeal Carbon Dioxide Removal in Patients With Acute Kidney Injury</official_title>
  <sponsors>
